<item>
            <title>[HBASE-17234] Allow alternate Readers/Writers; currently hardcoded</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-17234</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Allow alternate HFile Reader and Writers. For Writers, we have WriterFactory so you&apos;d think it possible to supply a different Writer but in actuality, WriterFactory is hardcoded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Read side does something else altogether complicated by fact that Reader presumes trailer and that it has to take a Stream.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yeah, expecting someone would provide their own Reader/Writer is a little unexpected.... but....&lt;/p&gt;</description>
